  <brief_title>Lidocaine Gel 2% and Muscle Traction Pain During Squint Surgery in Pediatrics</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Applying Xylocaine Gel 2% to the Eye Preoperatively in Pediatrics Undergoing Squint Surgeries on Oculocardiac Reflex Intraoperatively and Postoperative Pain and Agitation: Cohort Study</official_title>
